{"tid":211254,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"無動力再試多次一齊","createTime":"2017-04-21T13:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T04:44:23.000Z","uid":72330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"902fecb6507105251462c3413b924951a0bcc5b0","tid":211254,"uid":72330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:36:35.000Z","msg":"近來同男朋友分左手<br />\n(因為我地價值觀好唔同<br />\n同我做左啲挑戰左佢底線嘅野<br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月每次見面基本上都會嘈交<br />\n但近來其實係有好轉<br />\n不過都捱唔過<br />\n<br />\n我仲係好鐘意佢<br />\n成日都想搵返佢復合<br />\n佢都承認對我仲有感覺<br />\n<br />\n咁我叫佢比多次機會我 再試過一齊<br />\n如果真係再唔得先真正分手<br />\n但佢話無動力再試多次<br />\n叫我放手 話一齊好辛苦<br />\n話做返朋友...<br />\n我應承左佢做返朋友<br />\n但其實心入面仲好唔捨得<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得係咪都無可能再一齊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a826b57a39920c03c4bd6968be59da106f783bb","tid":211254,"uid":72330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:47:23.000Z","msg":"有無人可以解答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好煩惱日日都好傷心<br />\n喺到掛住之前啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f35bd356740379bc936c7ea9b5b6477f60e005","tid":211254,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:49:01.000Z","msg":"做左咩挑戰佢底線？"},{"pid":"1f40b447432146665d25967bbc2d0ec4e046bc87","tid":211254,"uid":72330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做左咩挑戰佢底線？</blockquote><br />\n偷睇佢whatsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢好注重私隱"},{"pid":"50fd745a532926d5a4c9a84139456f433a9f2610","tid":211254,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:52:02.000Z","msg":"你地一齊左幾耐？"},{"pid":"afe914ce4865a24bb96ca73aa9c1a635282a28f8","tid":211254,"uid